    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's exactly the tone I was looking for. It really captures that 19th-century mindset. To wrap up the scene, could you have him conclude with a final thought on the inherent biological or natural differences that he believes necessitate this kind of European intervention? Just to really hammer home his justification for why this is \"natural\" or \"meant to be.\"",
